OL,3,C'Parents will be horrified': Sexual
OL,4,Charassment and sexism 'rife' in schools
OL,6,FAround one in seven school staff also
OL,7,Freported they had witnessed sexual
OL,8,Fharassment in their workplace in the
OL,9,Fpast five years.
OL,11,FTwo in five staff who witnessed
OL,12,Fabusive incidents did not report them
OL,13,Fbecause they felt it was "pointless"
OL,14,For could affect their career, said the
OL,15,Freport.
OL,17,FUnison general secretary Christina
OL,18,FMcAnea said: "Parents will be
OL,19,Fhorrified to learn their children are
OL,20,Fbeing taught in such toxic
OL,21,Fenvironments.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
