OL,3,C'Parents will be horrified': Sexual
OL,4,Charassment and sexism 'rife' in schools
OL,6,F"The danger is that language and
OL,7,Fbehaviour learned at an early age stay
OL,8,Fwith pupils as they become adults and
OL,9,Fgo out into the wider world.
OL,11,F"Any male staff with such outdated
OL,12,Fattitudes needs to think carefully
OL,13,Fabout how they interact with
OL,14,Fcolleagues and pupils.
OL,16,F"They must ditch such highly
OL,17,Finappropriate behaviour immediately.
OL,18,FBut clearly, schools can't tackle this
OL,19,Fhuge problem on their own.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
