OL,3,C'Parents will be horrified': Sexual
OL,4,Charassment and sexism 'rife' in schools
OL,6,F"Parents have a proper role to play
OL,7,Ftoo. Sexist and demeaning words have
OL,8,Fno place in the modern class or staff
OL,9,Froom.
OL,11,F"The role of misogynist influencers
OL,12,Fcannot be overstated. A solution must
OL,13,Fbe found before this worrying issue
OL,14,Fspirals out of control."
OL,16,FNina Humphries of Feminista, which
OL,17,Fhelped with the report, added: "It is
OL,18,Fdeeply concerning that misogyny is so
OL,19,Fnormalised in schools.
