OL,3,C'Parents will be horrified': Sexual
OL,4,Charassment and sexism 'rife' in schools
OL,6,F"This fuels violence against women and
OL,7,Fgirls and limits the aspirations of
OL,8,Fall young people.
OL,10,F"These joint survey results contribute
OL,11,Fto the abundance of evidence that
OL,12,Fsexism and sexual harassment are rife
OL,13,Fin the UK education system.
OL,15,F"Staff and students alike face this
OL,16,Funacceptable behaviour. More must be
OL,17,Fdone to make schools and colleges
OL,18,Fsafer."
